1. *Snagu* mi daje vera u Boga. (My faith in God gives me strength.)
2. Zdravlje je najveća *snaga* organizma. (Health is the greatest strength of the body.)
3. Pobednik je onaj koji ima *snagu* da se bori. (The victor is the one who has the strength to fight.)
4. Ova knjiga je prepuna *snage* i optimizma. (This book is full of strength and optimism.)
5. U teškim situacijama potrebna je *snaga* volje. (In difficult situations, strength of will is needed.)
6. Naša porodica je naša najveća *snaga*. (Our family is our greatest strength.)